uilder makes it simple to create documentation formats that match your specific practice needs.</p></div><div class="bg-cyan-50 rounded-2xl p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300"><div class="w-12 h-12 bg-teal-200 text-teal-700 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4 font-bold text-xl">2</div><h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-3 font-poppins">Building Confidence</h3><p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Start with a few encounters using AI Scribe to become familiar with the workflow. Most providers find the system intuitive and begin seeing immediate benefits in their first few uses.</p></div><div class="bg-green-50 rounded-2xl p-6 hover:shadow-lg transition-shadow duration-300"><div class="w-12 h-12 bg-green-200 text-green-700 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-4 font-bold text-xl">3</div><h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-800 mb-3 font-poppins">Ongoing Support</h3><p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">We value your feedback and are here to help if you need assistance. Our support resources include detailed documentation, video guides, and direct support channels to ensure you get the most value from AI Scribe.</p></div></div><div class="text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto"><p class="text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">The system is designed to integrate seamlessly into your existing workflow, allowing you to focus on what matters most: providing excellent patient care with comprehensive documentation support.</p></div></div></div></section><section class="py-16"><div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 transition-all duration-700 opacity-0 translate-y-10"><div class="bg-teal-600 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 text-center text-white max-w-6xl mx-auto shadow-xl"><h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4 font-poppins">Klinik Dokümantasyonunuzu Dönüştürmeye Hazır mısınız?</h2><p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-white/95 mb-8 font-raleway leading-relaxed">AI Scribe ile uygulama iş akışlarını d